# Univ Project Overview

- Project: `univ` ([github.com/univ4/app](https://github.com/univ4/app))
- Goal: Family-only AI college admission consulting dashboard for a Korean high school senior.
- Student profile: mock exam grade 1-2, school grade 2-3, target `서강대/성균관대/한양대` engineering track.
- Core users:
  - Dad: `Admin` (data input, strategy decisions)
  - Son: `Viewer` (results, chatbot, schedule)
  - Mom: `Viewer` (monitoring)
  - Friends: `Viewer` (read-only share scope when allowed)
- Team and schedule:
  - Single developer (dad)
  - 4-week MVP focused on P0 features

## Product Principles

- This is a practical family decision-support tool, not a commercial SaaS.
- Show evidence and explain uncertainty; do not imply guaranteed admission.
- Prefer fast iteration and clear UX over over-engineering.
